    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The facets are dynamic based on the result set. Removing `isRefined` means that the selected values may disappear, which is also confusing for users. I think that there is no perfect solution here, but at least end-users (not devs) will be less confused by moving values than disappearing values.",
